							<h2 id="k-Page-titleHTML-151-h2"><span class="in">Why ECSP</span></h2>
<!-- Text Page Contents -->
<div class="article">
	<div class="article-content">
<!-- Rich Text Element -->
<div id="k-Element-richTextHTML-150" class="RichTextElement">
<p><span style="font-family: Times; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Georgia; font-size: 12px;">ECSP is the only Distributor in Japan that can migrate your business strategy over time to meet the changing needs of your company.&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p>Many companies get off to a great start with a Distributor but as the business grows there may be a need for more control. The Distributor has no incentive to work with you to achieve this, often causing a significant reduction in sales, as they own the channel. It often means starting the business development over again.</p>
<p>ECSP is different. ECSP can start as your Distributor, and as<span style="font-family: Times; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Georgia; font-size: 12px;">&nbsp;revenues grow ECSP will work with you to migrate to a direct model, and eventually to a subsidiary with full time employees. No other Distributor in Japan has a business model to achieve this.</span></span></p>
<p>If your company is considering entering the Japanese market, or if are just getting started with a few Resellers, contact us today.&nbsp;</p>
</div>
